@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jtkwsp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.03 - v1 + 0.04)) - wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.10)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.13 - tmp + 0.35) - v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.09 / v2 + 0.02) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.54)))
    v2 = wp.abs(0.07)
    data[tid] = v0
